<li><a href="http://bjr.birjournals.org/cgi/reprint/Supplement_27/1/41.pdf" class="external text" title="http://bjr.birjournals.org/cgi/reprint/Supplement_27/1/41.pdf" rel="nofollow">Radiation accidents with multi-organ failure in the United States</a></li>
